verses.1: Topa ka phat ding hi. Topa ka Pasian aw, nang na lian mahmah hi. Minthanna le liatna nang na silh hi.
verses.2: Puanza tawh tuam bangin khuavak tawh na kituam a, vantungte pen puanbuk bangin na zal hi.
verses.3: Van a om tui tungah na inn na lam a, na leeng dingin meiipite na bawl a, huih khate tungah nang na tuang hi.
verses.4: Na kamtai dingin huihte na bawl a, mei le meikuangte na nasemte na hisak hi.
verses.5: Leitung a liing ngei lo dingin ama bulpi tungah na phut hi.
verses.6: Nangmah in puan tawh tuam bangin leitung pen tui thukpi tawh na tuam a, tuate in mualte tuumcip hi.
verses.7: Na thuhilhna hangin tua tuite tai khia uh a, na thupiakna awging a zak uh ciangin kikhawh khia uh hi.
verses.8: Mual tung le guam sungah tua tuite luang uh a, amau adingin na seh sa munah a tung uh hi.
verses.9: Tua tuite in leitung a tuamkik loh nadingin amauteʼ kantan loh ding gamgi khat na phut hi.
verses.10: Kuamte sung panin ciktui na phul khiasak a, mualte kikalah a luang uh hi.
verses.11: Gamlak ganhingteʼ dawn ding tui na pia a, gamlak sakolte in a dangtakna uh tua tui ah a phasak uh hi.
verses.12: Tua tui kiangah huihlak vasate om uh a, sing hiangte lakah amaute ham zaizai uh hi.
verses.13: A sangna mun na omna panin mite tungah guah na zusak a, nangma thupha tawh leitung a kidim hi.
verses.14: Nangmah in ganhingte adingin lopa, mihing in leilak panin an a ngah theih nadingin a khawh ding ankungte,
verses.15: mihing lungsim a nuamsak ding leenggahzu, mihing maitang a zolsak ding sathau, mihing lungsim a hatsak ding an na piangsak hi.
verses.16: Topa in a suan, Lebanon mual a om taamtak singte, tua ama singkungte in guahtui tampi a ngah hi.
verses.17: Tua singte tungah vasate in bu bawl uh a, taksing kungte lakah gunvapite in bu a tom uh hi.
verses.18: Mual sangte pen sathakte ading hi a, suangtumte pen sakhiteʼ belh ding ahi hi.
verses.19: Hun ciamteh nadingin khapi na bawl a, ni in zong a tum ding hun a thei hi.
verses.20: Nangmah in khuamial na bawl a, gamlak ganhing khempeuh a vak khiat hun pen zan hunsung ahi hi.
verses.21: Humpinelkai khanglaite in amauʼ nek ding sa a ngah nadingun nakpi takin hawk uh a, amauʼ an ding Pasianʼ tung pan a ngah uh hi.
verses.22: Ni a suah ciangin amaute kihem khia uh a, a kua sung uh ah a lum hithiat uh hi.
verses.23: Mite pen nasem dingin kuan khia uh a, nitak mateng na sem uh hi.
verses.24: Topa aw, na sep sa nate tam mahmah hi. Nangmah in ciimna tawh tuate khempeuh na bawl a, na piansak ganhingte tawh leitung a kidim hi.
verses.25: Hua lai ah, ganhing a lian a neu, sim zawh lohin a tam, a vak muamua-na, lianin a zai mahmah tuipi om hi.
verses.26: Hua tuipi tungah teembawte le gualnop nadingin na bawl Awle a pai hi.
verses.27: A hun ciangin an na piak ding ngakin hihte khempeuh in nangmah hong en uh hi.
verses.28: Na piak ciangin amaute in ne uh a, an na pia a, amaute lungkim uh hi.
verses.29: Na maitang na seel ciangin amaute khasia uh hi. Amauʼ husanna na lakkhiat ciangin amaute si-in amauʼ pianna leivui ah a ciahkik uh hi.
verses.30: Na hu na sankhiat ciangin amaute a kipiangsak hi a, nangmah in leitung na bawl thak hi.
verses.31: Leitung a et ciangin tua leitung kiliingin, mualte a lawn ciangin tua mualte meikhu a suak, ama nasepna ah Topa lungdam henla, Topaʼ minthanna kip tawntung tahen.
verses.33: Ka nuntak lai teng Topa tungah la ka sa dinga, ka hin lai teng ka Pasian phatna la ka sasa ding hi.
verses.34: Topa in hong lungdamsak ahih manin ka lasaknate in zong amah lungdamsak tahen.
verses.35: Leitung panin mawhnei mite bei mang henla, migilote om nawn kei hen. Keʼn, Topa ka phat ding hi. Topa ka phat ding hi.
